/insider-selling_96.jpg"}, {"size": "thumb", "url": "https://cdn.benzinga.com/files/imagecache/250x187xUP/images/story/2012/insider-selling_96.jpg"}], "source": "", "summary": "When insiders sell shares, it indicates their concern in the company’s prospects or that they view the stock as being overpriced. Either way, this signals an opportunity to go short on the stock. Insider sales should not be taken as the only indicator for making an investment or trading decision. At best, it can lend conviction to a selling decision.", "symbols": ["CIEN", "COIN", "LSXMA", "ORCL", "TZOO"], "updated_at": "2021-12-28T12:30:28Z", "url": "https://www.benzinga.com/news/21/12/24792942/5-stocks-insiders-are-selling"}, {"author": "Charles Gross", "content": "", "created_at": "2021-12-28T16:58:30Z", "headline": "Oracle Option Alert: Jan 21 $100 Calls Sweep (32) above Ask!: 1893 @ $0.17 vs 11047 OI; Ref=$89.0", "id": 24799527, "images": [], "source": "", "summary": "", "symbols": ["ORCL"], "updated_at": "2021-12-28T16:58:30Z", "url": "https://www.benzinga.com/markets/options/21/12/24799527/oracle-option-alert-jan-21-100-calls-sweep-32-above-ask-1893-0-17-vs-11047-oi-ref-89-0"}, {"author": "Shanthi Rexaline", "content": "", "created_at": "2021-12-29T16:56:15Z", "headline": "10 Tech Predictions For 2022: Nasdaq At 19K, Apple AR/VR Glasses, Metaverse Becomes Reality And More", "id": 24719992, "images": [{"size": "large", "url": "https://cdn.benzinga.com/files/imagecache/2048x1536xUP/images/story/2012/cloud-3805852_1920_23.png"}, {"size": "small", "url": "https://cdn.benzinga.com/files/imagecache/1024x768xUP/images/story/2012/cloud-3805852_1920_23.png"}, {"size": "thumb", "url": "https://cdn.benzinga.com/files/imagecache/250x187xUP/images/story/2012/cloud-3805852_1920_23.png"}], "source": "", "summary": "Notwithstanding near-term weakness, tech stocks are on a multiyear rally, giving rise to fears of a long-overdue correction, Wedbush analyst Daniel Ives said in a note.\n\nThe near-term sel